VALUES ('Call of Duty Warzone', 'Battle Royale', 9, 0, 'pc,xbox,playstation', 'Warzone allows online multiplayer combat among 150 players, although some limited-time game modes support 200 players. The game features both cross-platform play and cross-platform progression between three games. The game features three main modes: Plunder, Resurgence, and Battle Royale.');

